        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Beginning with that blessed and holy hour when a kiss betrothed these two souls, Marius was there every evening.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "If, at that period of her existence, Cosette had fallen in love with a man in the least unscrupulous or debauched, she would have been lost; for there are generous natures which yield themselves, and Cosette was one of them. One of woman's magnanimities is to yield.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Love, at the height where it is absolute, is complicated with some indescribably celestial blindness of modesty.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Often you give the heart, and we take the body.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Your heart remains with you, you gaze upon it in the gloom with a shudder.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Love has no middle course; it either ruins or it saves.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "All human destiny lies in this dilemma.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "This dilemma, ruin, or safety, is set forth no more inexorably by any fatality than by love.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Love is life, if it is not death.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Cradle; also coffin.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "The same sentiment says \"yes\" and \"no\" in the human heart.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000004_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000004_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Of all the things that God has made, the human heart is the one which sheds the most light, alas! and the most darkness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "God willed that Cosette's love should encounter one of the loves which save.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "They touched each other, they gazed at each other, they clasped each other's hands, they pressed close to each other; but there was a distance which they did not pass.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Not that they respected it; they did not know of its existence.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Marius was conscious of a barrier, Cosette's innocence; and Cosette of a support, Marius' loyalty.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "The first kiss had also been the last.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000006_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000006_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "She refused nothing, and he asked nothing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000006_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000006_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Cosette was happy, and Marius was satisfied.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000006_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000006_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "They lived in this ecstatic state which can be described as the dazzling of one soul by another soul.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000006_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000006_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "It was the ineffable first embrace of two maiden souls in the ideal.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000006_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000006_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Two swans meeting on the Jungfrau.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "At that hour of love, an hour when voluptuousness is absolutely mute, beneath the omnipotence of ecstasy, Marius, the pure and seraphic Marius, would rather have gone to a woman of the town than have raised Cosette's robe to the height of her ankle.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Once, in the moonlight, Cosette stooped to pick up something on the ground, her bodice fell apart and permitted a glimpse of the beginning of her throat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "What took place between these two beings?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Nothing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "They adored each other.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "All flowers unfolded around them and sent them incense; and they opened their souls and scattered them over the flowers.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "The wanton and vigorous vegetation quivered, full of strength and intoxication, around these two innocents, and they uttered words of love which set the trees to trembling.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
