        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Cosette said to Marius:--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "[In all this and athwart this celestial maidenliness, and without either of them being able to say how it had come about, they had begun to call each other thou.]",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "My name is Euphrasie.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "\"Euphrasie?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "But my real name is Euphrasie.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "\"Yes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "\"Do you like it better than Euphrasie?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "On another occasion she gazed intently at him and exclaimed:--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "And Marius, in the very heavens, thought he heard a strain sung by a star.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "I want you to be well, because, in the first place, if you were not well, I should be very unhappy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "And this was simply divine.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Once Marius said to Cosette:--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "In the middle of another conversation, he chanced to exclaim:--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "He would have been obliged to speak to Cosette of her garter, and that was impossible. This bordered on a strange theme, the flesh, before which that immense and innocent love recoiled with a sort of sacred fright.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "During this time, clouds passed above their heads.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000032_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000032_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Every time that the wind blows it bears with it more of the dreams of men than of the clouds of heaven.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "This chaste, almost shy love was not devoid of gallantry, by any means. To pay compliments to the woman whom a man loves is the first method of bestowing caresses, and he is half audacious who tries it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "A compliment is something like a kiss through a veil.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000033_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000033_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Voluptuousness mingles there with its sweet tiny point, while it hides itself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000033_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000033_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "The heart draws back before voluptuousness only to love the more.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000033_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000033_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Marius' blandishments, all saturated with fancy, were, so to speak, of azure hue.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000033_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000033_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "The birds when they fly up yonder, in the direction of the angels, must hear such words.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000033_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000033_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "There were mingled with them, nevertheless, life, humanity, all the positiveness of which Marius was capable.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "You are a grace.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000034_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000034_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "I know not what is the matter with me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000034_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000034_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "The hem of your gown, when the tip of your shoe peeps from beneath, upsets me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000034_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000034_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "You talk astonishingly good sense.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "And Cosette answered:--",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "\"I have been loving a little more all the time that has passed since this morning.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Cosette's whole person was ingenuousness, ingenuity, transparency, whiteness, candor, radiance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "It might have been said of Cosette that she was clear.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000038_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000038_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "She produced on those who saw her the sensation of April and dawn.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "It was quite simple that Marius should admire her, since he adored her. But the truth is, that this little school girl, fresh from the convent, talked with exquisite penetration and uttered, at times, all sorts of true and delicate sayings.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Her prattle was conversation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000039_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000039_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "She never made a mistake about anything, and she saw things justly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000039_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000039_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "The woman feels and speaks with the tender instinct of the heart, which is infallible.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "No one understands so well as a woman, how to say things that are, at once, both sweet and deep.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "Sweetness and depth, they are the whole of woman; in them lies the whole of heaven.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000041_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000041_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4513",
        "content": "The most sovereign symptom of love is a tenderness that is, at times, almost unbearable.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4513_16024_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4513/16024/4513_16024_000043_000000.wav",
